title: Cast of 1Up Play Would You Rather: Gamer Edition

media:group.media:title: Cast of 1Up Play Would You Rather: Gamer Edition
media:group.media:description:
Would you rather be an Orc or an Elf? Or would you rather get beaten by a 9 year old or a grandma? We ask all the tough questions.

In celebration of the movie '1UP,' we went behind the scenes with the cast to play a little "Would You Rather." Do you agree with their answers? Watch to find out, and check out '1UP' on Prime Video starting July 15.

Cast:
Paris Berelc
Taylor Zakhar Perez
Hari Nef
Lolita Melina
Madison Baines
DJ Mausner
Nicholas Coombe
Stephen Joffe
